0.body: This mdBook is a personal collection of more or less useful little things that I have learned from day to day. It is not a blog. The contributions should all be relatively short and reduced to the essentials. It is also a tool to consolidate new knowledge and a quick reference point at the same time. The project is inspired by jbranchaud/til . Thanks a lot for the amazing work! ( How I Built a Learning Machine )
